16	 * [1] B. C. Carlson, ed., Chapter 19 in "Digital Library of Mathematical
17	 *     Functions," NIST, US Dept. of Commerce.
18	 *     https://dlmf.nist.gov/19.16.E1
19	 * [2] B. C. Carlson, "Numerical computation of real or complex elliptic
20	 *     integrals," Numer. Algorithm, vol. 10, no. 1, pp. 13-26, 1995.
